icons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Martial, Baby, MARTIAL.</span><br>  Posts: 562<br> <font color=#660000>(3/8/02 4:25:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bows</span><hr size=1> I don't know but let us know, will ya? =)  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=trentalkaline>Trent Alkaline</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 134<br> <font color=#660000>(3/8/02 9:58:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bows</span><hr size=1> id also be very interested in hearing how this works out, im starting to play with bows a bit, level 86 right now, toying with a ql 47 urban crossbow right now, got about 200 in bow, 100 in fling 100 in aimed <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ujulei.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Julei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#660000>(3/19/02 6:08:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bows</span><hr size=1> The Schuyler Bow was introduced in 13.8. I don't know where it drops, but I imagine the Trader shops, most new weapons in 13.8 seems to come from there (except the stuff that drops in Camelot). Anyone tried the Schuyler Bow? It only requires Bow skill, has good clip and fairly good max damage. See links below for stats:<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://antiguardians.org/itemdb.php?&cmd=view&id=159021">antiguardians.org/itemdb....&id=159021</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://antiguardians.org/itemdb.php?&cmd=view&id=159022">antiguardians.org/itemdb....&id=159022</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=znail>Znail</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#660000>(3/19/02 7:52:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bows</span><hr size=1> Yeah, this is interesting.. have heard about bows criting 10k ... dunno if its just a load of BS... <br><br>also looked at that new Schuyler bow from 13.8 looks quite nice...although the crit isnt that impressive..<br><br>And also logged on with my trader yesterday... long time since last... just to look in those new trader shops... <br><br>I didnt see any bows.. only the True Katanas some new piercing thingy.. dont remember the name.. and the new ADV pistols... all of them looks quite ok... but noone with MA req... <br>gonna travell some tonight and see if the traders shops differ from town to town..<br><br>funny thing though.. those items in tradershop goes all the way up to ql 146...<br><br><br>cson..is that a ql 200 pow bow? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=znail>Znail</A> at: 3/19/02 7:54:56 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ucson777.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cson777</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 176<br> <font color=#660000>(3/19/02 10:44:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> The Schuyler Bow was infact the bow being exploited by the crats. But it could have been done with any bow. There was a way to stack an item that gave bonuses to the bow skill, thus giving a person 10k to bow skill. There was also an exploit to stack your token board, giving you 1000% or more Exp bonus. So killing something that would normally give you 50k XP would now give you 500k XP.<br><br>The exploit was fixed with the emergency patch, and I'm sure the exploiters are looking for similar ways to cheat. I found out about it on hackersquest after the patch.<br><br>Anyways, the stats above are from a QL 200 pow bow. I'm also looking at other weapons such as the Ultra-light Missile Pistol and Lovemaker rifle. I haven't decided yet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ukeil2000.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Keil2000</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#660000>(3/19/02 7:48:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Ubran crossbow:<br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://antiguardians.org/itemdb.php?&cmd=view&id=125061">antiguardians.org/itemdb....&id=125061</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>What you will notice is the quick delay to equip or unequip this bow.  This would be the best bow to invest in for a MA.  It is a bit slow, but you will have a ranged attack that you can swap in/out very fast. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/bthepunchingbag74708.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=xer>Xer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#660000>(3/21/02 10:05:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> Hmmm.. Bow, AS, and FS?  Thats a lot of IP to spend just for a bow. <br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/usukanilirilith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SukAnil Irilith</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.random.fool.btinternet.co.uk/images/SAmini.JPG" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#660000>(3/21/02 6:43:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.random.fool.btinternet.co.uk/images/SukAnil.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> I've just picked one of those up in a mission, and i'm thinking about using it as a pulling tool once i next level. The snipe ability is nice too, with a heavy investment in concealment being on my list of things to try.<br><br>Mind you, that relys on me being able to level, i got killed twice by incompetent party members the last time i was on. One guy who claimed he had been playing since Beta was easily the worst team member i have ever had the misfortune of meeting. I mean, a nano MP with a hammer, who then pulled the heal pet off me cos he managed to pull aggro and didn't put it back on me when i taunted the target, hence i go down and he stands there going 'why are you dead?'<br><br>I wanted to break the hammer over his stupid head and scream 'just stay out of the way!' at him<br><br>I think i'm going to write a guide to teaming<br><br>Tathiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/usukanilirilith.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SukAnil Irilith</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.random.fool.btinternet.co.uk/images/SAmini.JPG" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#660000>(3/21/02 7:25:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.random.fool.btinternet.co.uk/images/SukAnil.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> oh, has anyone tried the <a href="http://antiguardians.org/itemdb.php?cmd=search&name=Venom+Compound+Bow&nano=0">Venom Compound Bow</a>?<br><br>Mainly asking because i belive Chemical AC is broken <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ujulei.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Julei</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tiny Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#660000>(3/25/02 5:08:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> I'm a Fixer, using a Mausser Chemical Streamer, and I have no reason to believe Chemical AC is broken. What makes you think it is? <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=471.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=471.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=471.topic&index=10><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=471.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.threadControl?topicID=471.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=471.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=471.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub83.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thepunchingbag74708frm4">House Rules<option value="thepunchingbag74708frm1">Main Dojo<option value="thepunchingbag74708frm2">All About Gear<option value="t